            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had admitted my child thinking it to be run be Zee. But during admission they cheated me by the assurance that it was part of Zee group when in reality Saini Education trust had already terminated the contract with Zee and had renamed the school Saini International School. Raka ma'am and Piyali ma'am have resigned due to this. They were the reason the students were so discipline. Zee had a firm grip on the running of the school which guaranteed quality in education.  The school is not Mount Litera Zee School,  it is Saini International School.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
